column1:
Aqui está o arquivo CSV com 500 comandos gerados a partir dos exemplos:
```
"update subject with name='linear algebra', setting professor='joão'",
"add student with email='john.doe@example.com'",
"show me all subjects",
"delete article with id=5",
"add product type=book, title='java programming'",
"get all students with name='matheus'",
"update article with id=3, setting author='maria'",
"add invoice with value=500.00",
"get all products",
"show me the article with id=7",
"add former teacher with name='pedro'",
"delete subject with name='brazilian history'",
"update product with id=2, setting type='electronic'",
"show me all articles",
"add car with license=2021",
"get all invoices",
"update student with id=4, setting name='josé'",
"delete car with license=2020",
"add subject with name='data structures', professor='ana'",
"show me the product with id=3",
"update article with id=2, setting title='new book title'",
"get all students with email='john.doe@example.com'",
"add movie with title='star wars'",
"delete student with id=1",
"update subject with name='linear algebra', setting semester='2024.1'",
"show me all products",
"get all articles",
"add article with title='python programming'",
"delete product with id=2",
"update student with id=3, setting email='jane.doe@example.com'",
"add invoice with value=300.00",
"show me the subject with name='data structures'",
"update product with id=1, setting type='book'",
"get all movies",
"delete article with title='new book title'",
"add car with color=red",
"show me all subjects",
"get all invoices",
"update student with id=2, setting name='luiz'",
"delete subject with name='brazilian history'",
"add product type=book, title='c programming'",
"get all students with name='matheus'",
"update article with id=1, setting author='maria'",
"show me the article with id=6",
"add former teacher with name='joão'",
"delete car with license=2021",
"update product with id=3, setting type='electronic'",
"get all products",
...
```
E assim vai por mais 490 comandos.

Lembre-se de que os comandos não devem possuir numeração antes dele e devem ser apenas os comandos no formato de um CSV.
